descriptionHtml:
The one-stop destination for international news of the sport of Snooker. Get live updates of Snooker events from all around the world, global ranking updates, plus news and athlete profiles in an easy-to-use mobile application.

The Snooker News app gets the news from following sources:

** World Snooker News | The Official Website of World Snooker - Featuring the latest snooker scores, news and results, plus rankings, tournament calendar and player profiles.

** World Professional Billiards and Snooker Association (WPBSA) - The World Professional Billiards and Snooker Association Limited ('The WPBSA') is the governing body for both Snooker and Billiards worldwide. The WPBSA governs these sports through regulation and application of the rules of the association.

** Google News - Snooker - Snooker at Google News

** Reddit - Snooker - Reddit Snooker

** Grove Leisure - Blogs on Snooker management and player development.

** SnookerHQ - Reports and analysis from the world of professional snooker, with an additional focus on the Irish amateur scene.

** BBC Sport - Snooker - The home of Snooker on BBC Sport online. Includes the latest news stories, results, fixtures, video and audio.

** Snooker Canada - Their mission is to encourage players at all levels to enjoy and develop their skills within the game

** Snooker Hub - At the heart of the amateur game. Upcoming Snooker tournaments. Upcoming Snooker Exhibitions. Snooker News.

** Snooker, my love - Everything you need to know about the world of professional snooker and more.

** Snookertv.de - The TV Blog for World Snooker Main Tour - Live streams, links, events, rankings, Videos, News, Software, odds, results and more.

** St Blazey & District Snooker League - Welcome to the St Blazey & District Snooker Leagues Official website, where we be showing all the latest from the league as well as pro snooker articles from expert writers and images taken by professional photographers.

** Inside Snooker - A website dedicated to providing news, comment and in-depth analysis on the professional snooker world
